---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Stay for Professionals — Preserve Your Expertise">
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <p class="text-ember text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">For Professionals</p>
        <h1 class="heading-lg mb-6">
          Decades of expertise.<br/>
          <span class="text-ember">Preserved in your voice.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
          CEOs, doctors, lawyers, architects, consultants — your hard-won knowledge deserves to outlast your tenure. Capture your decision-making, your intuition, your wisdom.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Point -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">The cost of knowledge loss</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center mb-12">
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-serif text-ember mb-2">$31.5B</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-parchment-muted">Lost annually by Fortune 500 companies due to knowledge loss</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-serif text-ember mb-2">42%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-parchment-muted">Of institutional knowledge leaves when employees retire</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-serif text-ember mb-2">70%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-parchment-muted">Of expertise is tacit — never written down</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          When a senior executive, doctor, or expert leaves, decades of pattern recognition, relationship context, and hard-won judgment walks out the door. Stey helps capture what documents and SOPs never will.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-12">Who uses Stey for professional knowledge</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Executives & Founders</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Document strategic thinking, company history, key relationship context, and lessons learned. Create a knowledge base successors can reference long after you've moved on.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Why certain decisions were made</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Relationship history with key partners/clients</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Company culture and values context</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Medical Professionals</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Capture clinical intuition, rare case experiences, and patient care philosophy. The knowledge that can't be found in textbooks.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Diagnostic pattern recognition</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Rare case experiences and lessons</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Patient communication approaches</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Legal Professionals</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Document negotiation strategies, judge/court insights, and case learnings that young associates desperately need.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Negotiation tactics and timing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Client relationship management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Court-specific insights</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Consultants & Advisors</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Turn years of client work into a searchable knowledge base. The frameworks, the approaches, the lessons that make you valuable.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Problem-solving frameworks</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Industry-specific insights</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-ember mt-1">→</span>
                <span class="body-sm">Client engagement best practices</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <blockquote class="text-center">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-parchment mb-6 italic">
            "I've spent 35 years in medicine. I've seen cases most residents will never encounter. When I retire, I don't want all of that to just... disappear. Stey lets me capture the thinking behind the diagnosis, not just the diagnosis itself."
          </p>
          <cite class="text-parchment-muted">— Dr. James K., Retiring Surgeon</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 md:p-10 border border-ember/30">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Enterprise-grade privacy</h3>
              <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
                Professional knowledge often contains confidential information. Stey processes everything on-device — no data ever leaves your phone. No cloud servers, no risk of breach, full compliance with confidentiality requirements.
              </p>
              <a href="/privacy" class="text-ember hover:underline">Read our privacy policy →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-md mb-6">Your expertise deserves to outlast you.</h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted mb-8">
          Start capturing the knowledge only you possess.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-parchment text-void px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-ember transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
          </svg>
          Download for iOS — Free
        </a>
        <p class="text-parchment-dark text-sm mt-4">
          Enterprise licensing coming soon. <a href="/contact" class="text-ember hover:underline">Contact us</a> for early access.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
